Iimpepha zoGayo-zimvo ezi zisetyenziselwa ukuyilwa komgaqo-nkqubo yaye zilungiselelwa ukucacisela uluntu. Emva kwexesha lengcaciso, umgaqo-nkqubo ogqityiweyo uthi ushicilelwe kwiPhepha leNgcaiciso yoMgaqo-nkqubo.
Ikhonkco 'Lokufaka Izimvo' liya kuvela ukuba kukho naziphi na iimpepha zogayo-zimvo ezisavulelekileyo.
